---
// 光闇詞について（日本語版）
import { ClientRouter } from 'astro:transitions';
---
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>光闇詞について - 光闇詞</title>
    <meta name="description" content="哲学詩サイト『光闇詞』の成り立ちや、作者の思想について解説します。">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <ClientRouter />
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="main-title">光闇詞について</h1>
      <h2 class="sub-title">About "The Hymn of Light and Shadow"</h2>
    </header>

    <main class="content-area">
      <section class="prose">
        <p>
          『光闇詞』は、光と闇という対極的な概念を通じて、人間の心の在り方を探求する思索の旅です。
        </p>
        <p>
          このサイトが、あなたの明日を少しでも楽にすることを願って。
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="page-footer">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">戻る</a>
    </footer>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

<style>
  :root {
    --color-bg: #f4f1ea;
    --color-text: #2b2b2b;
    --color-accent: #b22222;
    --color-gold: #c5a059;
    --color-sub: #5c5248;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    background-image: url('/images/parchment-bg.svg');
    background-repeat: repeat;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 2.0;
    position: relative;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }



  .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .main-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gold);
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .sub-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
    color: var(--color-sub);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .content-area {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }
  .prose {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .page-footer {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .back-link {
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    color: var(--color-sub);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  }
  .back-link:hover {
    background-color: var(--color-text);
    color: var(--color-bg);
    border-color: var(--color-text);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }
  .back-link:active {
    transform: scale(0.95);
  }
</style>

<style>
  /* Entry Animation */
  body {
      animation: fadeInPage 0.8s ease forwards;
      opacity: 0;
  }
  @keyframes fadeInPage {
      from { opacity: 0; }
      to { opacity: 1; }
  }
</style>
